description.description:
1. Long Stream Practice Maps (100 - 170 BPM)
  2. Long Stream Practice Maps 2 (175 - 215 BPM)
  3. Long Stream Practice Maps 3 (217 - 250 BPM)
This mapset has no breaks or pauses in the streams, and there are multiple songs per BPM for added variety.

All songs are 2 minutes long, and the different songs of the same BPM are all the same note length.

The _ difficulty is to circumvent the file size limit, which is based on the length of the longest difficulty in the mapset.
